description:
Perform a performance audit of news.ycombinator.com, en.wikipedia.org, developer.mozilla.org, www.python.org, and docs.github.com. Export at least three HAR files containing the network data for these sites to ~/Documents/har_exports/. Create a performance summary report at ~/Documents/performance_report.json with the following structure for all five sites:
{
  "site_url": {
    "total_requests": <int>,
    "total_transfer_size_kb": <float>,
    "js_requests": <int>,
    "css_requests": <int>,
    "image_requests": <int>,
    "largest_resource_url": "..."
  }
}
